  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "I am Jesus&#39; little lamb, Ever glad at heart I am; For my Shepherd gently guides me, Knows my need, and well provides me, Loves me ev&#39;ry day the same, Even calls me by my name.",
    "v2": "Day by day, at home, away, Jesus is my Staff and Stay. When I hunger, Jesus feeds me, Into pleasant pastures leads me; When I thirst, He bids me go Where the quiet waters flow.",
    "v3": "Who so happy as I am, Even now the Shepherd&#39;s lamb? And when my short life is ended, By His angel host attended, He shall fold me to His breast, There within His arms to rest."
  },
